---
const schedulingLink = 'https://calendly.com/aldogustavomalasomma/15min';
const briefHref =
  'mailto:hello@copycodeai.online?subject=' + encodeURIComponent('Blueprint Sprint Request');
---

<section id="blueprint" class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-14 sm:px-8 lg:px-12" aria-labelledby="blueprint-title">
  <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-soft sm:p-8">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-700">Entry Offer</p>
    <p class="mb-2 mt-2 text-lg font-medium text-slate-600">Before you build, make sure your structure won’t break later.</p>
    <h2 id="blueprint-title" class="mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold text-ink-900">Start with Clarity</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">System & Compliance Blueprint Sprint — €950</p>
    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">In 7 days, you get a build-ready execution blueprint for your next implementation cycle.</p>
    <p class="mt-2 max-w-3xl text-slate-700">
      This is practical planning, not theory. You leave with a plan you can use right away.
    </p>

    <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
      <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-500" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>Clear AI architecture (what to build and why)</span></li>
      <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-500" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>GDPR-ready data-flow mapping</span></li>
      <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-500" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>Accessibility risk overview (EAA / WCAG)</span></li>
      <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-500" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>Execution priorities for your next sprint</span></li>
      <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-500" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>Delivery notes for immediate implementation</span></li>
      <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-brand-500" aria-hidden="true"></span><span>30-min recorded walkthrough</span></li>
    </ul>

    <div class="mt-7 flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row">
      <a
        href={schedulingLink}
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-brand-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-soft hover:bg-brand-700 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-brand-600 focus-visible:ring-offset-2"
      >
        Start with a 15-min Technical Assessment
      </a>
      <a
        href={briefHref}
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-slate-300 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800 hover:border-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-100 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-brand-600 focus-visible:ring-offset-2"
      >
        Request a Brief Review
      </a>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-2 text-xs font-normal text-slate-500">Fixed price. 7-day delivery. Written follow-up included.</p>
  </article>

  <section class="mt-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-soft" aria-labelledby="after-call-title">
    <h3 id="after-call-title" class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-700">What happens after the call</h3>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">Short call. Clear next steps. No vague follow-up.</p>
    <ol class="mt-3 grid gap-3 text-sm text-slate-700 md:grid-cols-3">
      <li class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3">15-min technical assessment</li>
      <li class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3">You receive a written summary with the main risks, priorities, and next steps</li>
      <li class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3">If there’s a fit, the Blueprint Sprint starts the following week</li>
    </ol>
  </section>
</section>
